title: Kennedy.2015.06.03.WS.SDTV.x264-XAiO
description:
"Kennedy" is a news panel show hosted by Kennedy Montgomery. Kennedy Montgomery is a libertarian that you may recognize from 90's MTV, Stossel, and the Independents.

_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2

Kennedy does her monologue on the USA Freedom Act, Rand Paul's filibuster.

Tonight's panel consists of TOM SHILLUE, DAGEN MCDOWELL, and JANICE DEAN. They're all cool with the NSA spying. Fights ensue. This segment is so good. It's 3 v 1. Woot.

The panel returns to talk about a California State Senate bill to provide healthcare for illegal immigrants. Less fighting this time. :'(. Next up, should you have to be 21 to start smoking?

Soccer player TIM HOWARD stops by to talk about soccer. the recent FIFA scandal, his career, etc.

Our panel returns. (kind of) Dagan McDowell leaves, BRIAN MORGANSTERN joins. First up Caitlyn Jenner & her new reality TV show. They move on to talk about Reagan. Then waking up early?

KIMBLERY GUILFOYLE of The Five stops by to talk about her new book "Making the case".

Kennedy tries to play goalie.
